    },
    {
      "id": "69ecf34800000000003f1bf0",
      "text": "謎解き2026/4/26",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1777136457,
      "updated": 1777136457
    },
    {
      "id": "69ecf34800000000003f1bf1",
      "text": ">[Cheetah_math https://x.com/Cheetah_math/status/2006998900540923988] #ちーたー謎",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1777136457,
      "updated": 1777136457
    },
    {
      "id": "69ecf34800000000003f1bf2",
      "text": "> [https://pbs.twimg.com/media/G9pIFsXaMAM0grE?format=jpg&name=medium#.png]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1777136457,
      "updated": 1777136457
    },
    {
      "id": "69ecf34800000000003f1bf3",
      "text": "\tまわすやつ[~ ふくびき]というイメージなんだが違いそう[nishio.icon]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1777136457,
      "updated": 1777136457
    },
    {
      "id": "69ecf34800000000003f1bf4",
      "text": "\t\t[~ 「ん」で終わることが想定されてそう]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1777136457,
      "updated": 1777136457
    },
    {
      "id": "69ecf34800000000003f1bf5",
      "text": "\t\t回すやつ、[~ ガラポン]か？[caki.icon]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1777136457,
      "updated": 1777136457
    },
    {
      "id": "69ecf34800000000003f1bf6",
      "text": "\t\t 答えの3の[~ 右上が欠けているので、たぶん濁点がつく]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1777136457,
      "updated": 1777136457
    },
    {
      "id": "69ecf34800000000003f1bf7",
      "text": "\t\t なるほど…なんか地域性がありそう[yosider.icon][nishio.icon]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1777136457,
      "updated": 1777136457
    },
    {
      "id": "69ecf34800000000003f1bf8",
      "text": "\t\tなるほど理解[terang.icon]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1777136457,
      "updated": 1777136457
    },
    {
      "id": "69ecf34800000000003f1bf9",
      "text": "\t\t\t[~ ガラポンでおｋ]と思う",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1777136457,
      "updated": 1777136457
    },
    {
      "id": "69ecf34800000000003f1bfa",
      "text": "\t✅",
